  <md:abstract>This module gives the need for greater frequency spectrum allocation for Mobile Communication and this has to be fulfilled within 350MHz to 3.5GHz considerable fraction of which is already occupied for TV usage.Hence ways and means have to be devised so that greater portion of this opportunity window is freed for Mobile Applications.</md:abstract>
